        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Clarifying Law Around Insurance of Marijuana Act or the CLAIM Act &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill generally provides a safe harbor from penalties or other adverse agency action for insurance companies that provide services to cannabis-related legitimate businesses in jurisdictions where such activity is legal. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The Government Accountability Office must report on barriers to marketplace entry for minority-owned and women-owned cannabis-related businesses.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
